IN	1/3 cup sour cream
IN	1/3 cup Vegenaise
IN	1/2 cup crumbled Gorgonzola cheese (use the picante or mountain kind, not the dulce)
IN	1/3 cup cold water
IN	1 tablespoon plus 1 teaspoon red wine vinegar
IN	1 large shallot, peeled and thinly sliced
IN	Big pinch coarse salt
IN	A few fresh grinds black pepper
PR	Stir everything together in a small bowl.
